quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,148,"Alla Yiɗaa ko feeñi ko e bone immorde e koŋngol, si wanaa on tooñaaɗo. Alla seeraani ko nanoow ko gannduɗo."
  4,149,"Si on peññinii moƴƴere, maa on cuuɗii nde maa on njaafima gah e bone, pellet, Alla seeraani jaafotooɗo kattanɗo."
  4,150,"Pellet, ɓeen won ɓe e yeddude Alla e Nulaaɓe Makko ɓeen, heɓe paala nde ɓe ceernndata hakkunde Alla e Nulaaɓe Makko ɓeen, heɓe mbia :"Miɗen gooŋɗina yoga min njedda yoga", heɓe paala jogitaade hakkunde ɗuum ɗoon laawol."
  4,151,"Ɓeen ɗoon ko kamɓe tigi ngoni yedduɓe ɓeen tigiri. Min kplalanii heeferɓe ɓe lepte koynooje."
  4,152,"Ɓeen gooɗinɓe Alla e Nulaaɓe Makko ɓe, ɓe ceerndaani hakkunde gooto e maɓɓe, ɓeen ɗoon, arma o weeɗ ɓe njoɓdi maɓɓe ndi. Alla seeraani jaafoto oɗo jurmotooɗo."
  4,153,"Yimɓe Defte ɓe no naamnoma nde njippintaa e dow maɓɓe deftere immorde e ka kammu ! Gooŋɗii ɓe naamninooma Muusaa ko ɓuri ɗuum mawnude : ɓe mbi'i : "Hollu amen Alla gite". Ŋa'as Ha'acaango ngo nanngiri ɓe sabu tooñannge maɓɓe nge. refti ɓe njogitii ngaari ndi(peeñɗi) ɓaawo nde ko ari eheɓe e ɓanngan- nduyeeji. Min njaafii gaay ɗum Min ngokki Muusaa hujja ɓannguɗo.(peeñɗo)"
  4,154,"Min ɓamtir dow maɓɓe Tuur fello ngo sabu ahadi maɓɓe ndii, min mbiani ɓe :"naatiree ka damal ko on naayiiɓe", Min mbi'ani ɓe : "Wata on njawtu(keerol) e asewe on", min nanngi e maɓɓe ahadi tekkundi."